347
00:32:17,800 --> 00:32:21,429
我不习惯投资我从没听说过的公司
I'm not in the habit of investing in companies I've never heard of.

348
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:29,676
George?Peter Williams 关于Vestron你知道多少?
George?Peter Williams.What do you know about Vestron?

349
00:32:34,160 --> 00:32:37,118
不 没什么 只是听到些传言 就这样
No problem.Just heard a whisper,that's all.

350
00:32:38,360 --> 00:32:41,193
不 有问题再找你
No.I'll call you if anything comes of it.

351
00:32:49,080 --> 00:32:50,513
好的 算我一份
Count me in.

352
00:32:51,640 --> 00:32:53,915
很好 还有件事...
Good.One more thing...

353
00:32:54,000 --> 00:32:57,231
我不想留下任何书面凭据 必须准备现金
I don't want to leave any paper trails.The money has to be in cash.

354
00:32:57,320 --> 00:32:58,753
