356
00:33:06,440 --> 00:33:08,908
感谢你给我这次机会
I just want to thank you for this opportunity.

357
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:10,638
- 我也是 - 谢谢
- Likewise. - Thank you.

358
00:33:39,240 --> 00:33:40,229
施点魔法
Work the spell.

359
00:33:55,560 --> 00:33:56,913
好啊
How're you doing?

360
00:33:59,120 --> 00:34:03,033
省省力气吧 我不会和工作伙伴发生关系的
Save us both a little time.I don't screw people I work with.

361
00:34:03,240 --> 00:34:04,229
- 不吗? - 不
- No? - No.

362
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:14,237
针对每个人...
Does that go for everyone?

363
00:34:15,280 --> 00:34:16,998
还是某一群人而已?
Or just the troops?

364
00:34:19,560 --> 00:34:21,949
给你个忠告 Danny 朋友的建议
Do you want a little tip,Danny?Some friendly advice?

365
00:34:22,040 --> 00:34:24,156
行 那太好了
Yeah,that would be great.

366
00:34:24,240 --> 00:34:28,199
边看边学 少管那些不归你管的事
Watch and learn.Stay out of things that don't concern you.

367
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:57,791
- 大家都在各忙各的 - 你很快就能融入这个大家族了
- Your guys seem pretty tight. - After a while,you get to be family.

368
00:35:00,400 --> 00:35:01,753
很好笑吗?
I say something funny?

369
00:35:01,840 --> 00:35:05,515
不是 这个家族并不是为我而生
No.The whole family thing works for me.

370
00:35:06,920 --> 00:35:08,672
你只是干小偷小摸的勾当 Danny
You play short cons,Danny.

371
00:35:08,760 --> 00:35:12,548
只会趁周末掏空别人的工资袋 你不会理解我们在干的事
Emptying people's wage packets on a Friday night.You wouldn't understand.

372
00:35:17,880 --> 00:35:20,440
- 可以提个意见吗? - 当然
- Can I make a criticism? - Okay.

373
00:35:22,600 --> 00:35:24,272
100,000
100,000?

374
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:28,234
我们能从那家伙身上搞到更多的钱
We can take this guy for a lot more than that.

375
00:35:28,320 --> 00:35:30,197
那正是你需要学的
That's the bit you don't get.

376
00:35:30,880 --> 00:35:32,552
并不是钱多钱少的问题
It's not just about the money.

377
00:35:32,640 --> 00:35:34,437
- 什么时候学? - 一直...
- Since when? - Since always.

378
00:35:34,560 --> 00:35:37,074
你不明白其中的道理 你什么也得不到
You don't get that,you don't get anything.

379
00:35:40,160 --> 00:35:42,754
我的长辈一直就是这么做的
My old man was as straight as they come.

380
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:47,071
安于现状 悠于生活
Never wanted much and life didn't disappoint him.

381
00:35:47,640 --> 00:35:49,710
他每天工作,吃饭,睡觉
He worked,ate,slept.

382
00:35:49,800 --> 00:35:52,360
按时纳税 中规中矩
Paid his taxes on time,toed the line.

383
00:35:53,040 --> 00:35:56,635
唯一的希望是能在60岁退休
The only dream he had was retiring at 60.

384
00:35:59,800 --> 00:36:04,191
结果就在60岁生日的前三天
Dropped dead in the Post Office three days before his 60th birthday.

385
00:36:05,640 --> 00:36:08,791
在邮局付电话帐单时 撒手人寰
He was paying his phone bill.

386
00:36:11,760 --> 00:36:13,955
- 真遗憾 - 是的 我也觉得
- I'm sorry. - Yeah.Me,too.

387
00:36:17,560 --> 00:36:20,438
你想做个普通人 是吗?
You want to be regular people?Do you?

388
00:36:20,760 --> 00:36:24,389
那就只能边抱怨工作的平凡无奇
Go do that.They're crying out for foot soldiers down there.

389
00:36:24,840 --> 00:36:28,799
边为那些老板,银行家,政客们卖命 仅此而已
Go and have your life run by bosses,bank managers,and politicians.

390
00:36:28,960 --> 00:36:31,428
但如果你真打算当个诈骗高手...
But if you want to be a grifter...

391
00:36:32,240 --> 00:36:36,028
不要带上任何 你无法及时摆脱的累赘
don't have anything in your life you can't walk away from in a second.

392
00:36:36,640 --> 00:36:39,473
爱人 朋友 甚至你的至亲
Lovers,friends,even your own mother.

393
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:45,793
那你妻子呢?
What about your wife?

394
00:36:48,560 --> 00:36:50,357
我听说了
I heard what happened.

395
00:36:51,320 --> 00:36:54,915
她想我做的 我做不到
She wanted me to be something I wasn't.

396
00:36:55,600 --> 00:36:58,068
我努力的不让她失望
And I was desperate not to disappoint her.

397
00:36:59,280 --> 00:37:00,872
谁想到 后患无穷
Recipe for disaster.

398
00:37:01,080 --> 00:37:02,911
如果你俩还在一起的话...
If you were still together...

399
00:37:03,000 --> 00:37:06,310
你能够做到对她视若无睹吗?
you're telling me you could just walk away from her?

400
00:37:08,840 --> 00:37:10,512
首要原则 Danny
First rule,Danny:

401
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:12,831
人不为己 天诛地灭
Always look after number one.

402
00:37:14,200 --> 00:37:16,589
人人都会这么做的
If you don't,no one else will.

403
00:37:20,840 --> 00:37:22,592
好的 我会铭记在心的
I'll try and remember that.

404
00:37:22,880 --> 00:37:25,314
回去吧 Danny 去休息会
Go home,Danny.Get some sleep.

405
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:48,353
Danny Blue?
Danny Blue.

406
00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:55,711
那孩子今天干得不错
The kid did well today.

407
00:37:57,920 --> 00:37:59,399
让我想起了当初的你
Reminds me of you.

408
00:38:00,640 --> 00:38:01,914
焦躁不安...
Worryingly.

409
00:38:03,440 --> 00:38:04,953
行了 别说了
Okay,come on.

410
00:38:05,960 --> 00:38:07,473
你怎么找到他的?
How did you find him?

411
00:38:07,800 --> 00:38:10,678
- 我有表现得这么明显吗? - 是你把我调教得太好了
- Am I that transparent? - You taught me well.

412
00:38:11,440 --> 00:38:13,874
我听说过他 他很棒
I heard about him.He's good.

413
00:38:14,600 --> 00:38:16,431
渴望成为行内最出色的
Wants to be the best.

414
00:38:17,840 --> 00:38:19,592
是不是听起来很熟悉?
That sound familiar?

415
00:38:20,200 --> 00:38:22,760
我让Eddie暗示他来找你
I told Eddie to point him in your direction.

416
00:38:22,920 --> 00:38:24,876
不管怎么说 我做到了
I'm all but done anyway.

417
00:38:26,720 --> 00:38:29,712
- 你打算不管他? - 我们都在努力摆脱
- You going to miss it? - We're all trying to get out.

418
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:32,951
如果你能做别的 你也想摆脱这种生活 不是嘛
You would,too,if you could think of something else to do.

419
00:38:37,880 --> 00:38:39,199
好啊 伙计们
All right,boys.

420
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:53,155
知道我为什么喜欢轮盘赌?
You know what I love about roulette?

421
00:38:53,960 --> 00:38:57,919
不到最后一秒 不知胜负结果
That glorious 30 seconds while the wheel is still spinning.

422
00:39:04,400 --> 00:39:05,913
<i>Christopher Rawlings</i>
<i>Christopher Rawlings.</i>

423
00:39:08,160 --> 00:39:09,957
因为那次赌马
The horseracing scam.

424
00:39:11,440 --> 00:39:14,159
他妻子发现他输了所有的积蓄
His wife found out he'd lost their life savings.

425
00:39:15,040 --> 00:39:17,190
他正在准备起诉
He's ready to press charges.

426
