These men are planning to swindle you out of your money.

469
00:43:49,680 --> 00:43:51,557
一定是搞错了
There must be some mistake.

470
00:43:53,680 --> 00:43:55,910
行了 Danny 没你的事了
All right,Danny.You can go.

471
