叛徒!
Judas.

472
00:44:00,880 --> 00:44:03,075
听着 事实不是这样的
Listen,this is not how it looks.

473
00:44:04,160 --> 00:44:05,309
把箱子拿过来
Get the cases.

474
00:44:15,560 --> 00:44:17,073
别这样 Michael
Don't do it,Michael.

475
00:44:17,400 --> 00:44:18,958
最后一课 Danny
Final lesson,Danny.

476
00:44:21,040 --> 00:44:22,234
我说真的
I mean it.

477
00:44:41,680 --> 00:44:43,671
- 哦 天哪! - 把他弄出去!
- Oh,God! - Get him out of here.

478
00:44:46,040 --> 00:44:47,268
该死!
Bastard!

479
00:44:49,200 --> 00:44:52,272
- 我们需要你的证词 - 我也有我考虑立场
- We need a statement. - I have my position to think of.

480
00:44:52,360 --> 00:44:55,477
- 先生 我们理解 - 把钱还给我 我立马走
- We understand that,sir. - Just give me my money and I'll go.

481
00:44:55,560 --> 00:44:59,951
- 我们不能这么做 那是证据 - 该死的钱 我要离开这里
- We can't do that,it's evidence. - Sod the money.Let me out of here.

482
00:45:00,040 --> 00:45:02,793
我不能被牵连到这种事里去 那会毁了我的
I can't be implicated in something like this.It'll ruin me.

483
00:45:02,880 --> 00:45:05,678
如果我们有足够的证据 就可以提起诉讼
If we have enough evidence,we can get guilty pleas.

484
00:45:05,760 --> 00:45:08,399
- 你不需要出庭 - 我被逮捕了吗?
- It won't go to court. - Am I under arrest?

485
00:45:08,480 --> 00:45:11,313
- 我们需要你的证词 - 我是不是被捕了?
- We need your statement. - Am I under arrest?

486
00:45:13,680 --> 00:45:14,954
没有 先生
No,sir.

487
00:45:17,800 --> 00:45:19,472
给我让开!
Get out of my way.

488
00:45:21,800 --> 00:45:23,153
让他走
Let him go.

489
00:45:31,200 --> 00:45:33,430
希望他清楚 他该做些什么
Let's hope the boss can do his stuff.

490
00:45:35,200 --> 00:45:36,713
很抱歉 弄伤了你
Sorry about the head.

491
00:45:58,080 --> 00:46:01,709
- 你杀了他 - 我救了你一命 Danny
- You killed him. - I saved your life,Danny.

492
00:46:03,400 --> 00:46:04,719
他们被拘留了
Everyone's in custody.

493
00:46:04,800 --> 00:46:07,189
回警察局时 我带你去检查下
We'll get you checked out on the way to the station.

494
00:46:07,280 --> 00:46:10,352

现在 有足够的时间结束我们的交易
First,time to keep your end of the bargain.

495
00:46:11,520 --> 00:46:13,954
确保没有任何遗漏
Be sure not to miss anything out.

496
00:46:17,360 --> 00:46:18,918
我没有背叛他们
I'm not a grass.

497
00:46:20,040 --> 00:46:21,473
放聪明点 Danny
Be smart,Danny.

498
00:46:22,080 --> 00:46:24,548
现在你只能认输了
All you can do now is lose.

499
00:46:25,840 --> 00:46:27,273
所以 我输了
Then I lose.

500
00:46:29,680 --> 00:46:32,752
迟早 我会好好整整象你这样 卑鄙无耻的家伙
I'd sooner that than hook up with a murdering scumbag like you.

501
00:46:32,840 --> 00:46:36,355
- Stone企图杀了你 - 他以为我背叛了他
- Stone fired a gun at you. - He thought I'd betrayed him.

502
00:46:37,720 --> 00:46:40,792
的确是 不然你就要进去蹲上五年
You do this,or I'll see you get five years.

503
00:46:42,000 --> 00:46:43,353
最后一次机会
Last chance.

504
00:46:46,520 --> 00:46:47,919
你去死吧!
Go screw yourself.

505
00:46:53,720 --> 00:46:55,950
好的 他合格了
Okay,he's all yours.

506
00:47:09,560 --> 00:47:11,596
我就知道你很棒 孩子
I knew you'd be okay,kid.

507
00:47:17,720 --> 00:47:20,029
- 我还没加入? - 现在 算上你了
- I don't get it. - You're all right.

508
00:47:21,600 --> 00:47:22,999
祝贺你!
Congratulations.

509
00:47:34,160 --> 00:47:36,674
<i>Sarge 那些犯人已经被释放了</i>
<i>Sarge,the prisoners you asked for are gone.</i>

510
00:47:36,760 --> 00:47:38,716
什么意思?被释放了?
What do you mean,they've gone?

511
00:47:39,200 --> 00:47:40,679
谁保释的?
Who signed them out?

512
00:47:41,120 --> 00:47:43,714
<i>这里显示是D.I.DePalma</i>
<i>It says here D.I.DePalma.</i>

513
00:48:12,080 --> 00:48:13,593
别这样 Michael
Don't do it,Michael.

514
00:48:14,080 --> 00:48:15,638
最后一课 Danny
Final lesson,Danny.

515
00:48:17,240 --> 00:48:18,514
我说真的
I mean it.

516
00:48:32,640 --> 00:48:34,278
给你看些东西
I got something for you.

517
00:48:53,360 --> 00:48:55,920
不知道怎么回事 就去搞清楚
If you don't know,find me someone who does.

518
00:48:56,000 --> 00:48:58,275
我想知道是谁派DePalma来的
I wanna know who sent DePalma over here.

519
00:48:58,360 --> 00:49:01,318
谁下的命令 谁是他的长官
Who gave him his orders,who his superior officer is.

520
00:49:05,880 --> 00:49:10,192
不 不用给我回电 我现在就要和他说话
No,you will not phone me back.I wanna speak to someone there now.

521
00:49:25,080 --> 00:49:27,116
Danny Blue Neil Cooper
Danny Blue.Neil Cooper.

522
00:49:27,640 --> 00:49:31,792
这个家伙 人称"诈骗艺术家"
This man defines the term "con artist."

523
00:49:31,960 --> 00:49:34,793
我刚加入 很高兴能帮上忙
I'm just passing through.Glad I could help.

524
00:49:36,040 --> 00:49:38,634
等一下!你对我开枪了?
Hang on a minute.You shot at me.

525
00:49:38,720 --> 00:49:40,915
是的 不过我射偏了 记得吗?
Yeah,but I missed,remember?

526
00:49:41,840 --> 00:49:43,910
所以我们现在是自由的
You're telling me we're home free?

527
00:49:54,080 --> 00:49:57,072
<i>绝对没错 除非警方想上庭解释</i>
<i>Absolutely.Unless the police would like to go to court...</i>

528
00:49:57,160 --> 00:50:00,277
<i>为什么会又罪犯 领导了这次调查工作</i>
<i>and explain how the investigation was led by one of the accused.</i>

529
00:50:04,800 --> 00:50:06,631
这就是原因 孩子
It's all in the detail,kid.

530
00:50:10,400 --> 00:50:11,719
干杯!
A toast.

531
00:50:14,800 --> 00:50:17,030
为Mickey Bricks的最后一案!
To Mickey Bricks' last score.

532
00:50:19,000 --> 00:50:20,638
一个时代的落幕
The end of an era.

533
00:50:26,400 --> 00:50:29,870
最甜蜜的谎言就是 一个骗子欺骗了另一个
The sweetest con of all is to con another grifter.

534
00:50:30,280 --> 00:50:32,669
而事实上 他不应该会上当
One who should know better.

535
00:50:36,760 --> 00:50:38,990
你是说 你并不打算收手?
You mean you're not retiring?

536
00:50:39,120 --> 00:50:41,759
我必须得找个理由 集合你们所有人
I had to say something to get you all together.

537
00:50:41,840 --> 00:50:44,115
你个小恶魔
You little devil.

538
00:50:44,200 --> 00:50:45,553
真是太聪明!
That's brilliant.

539
00:50:49,120 --> 00:50:52,271
那不仅仅是钱的问题 Mickey?
It's not all about the money,is it,Mickey?

540
00:50:52,360 --> 00:50:54,237
第一堂课结束了!
Here endeth the first lesson.

